<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/apr/21/">&#x27a0;</a> April 21, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="brdfdrcom-birdfeeder" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://brdfdr.com/">brdfdr.com (Birdfeeder)</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Dan Sandler&#8217;s research project, creating a protocol for distributed microblogging.  An improvement on identi.ca, as he built a Twitter gateway to help bootstrap.  Will definitely be playing with it tonight.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
